TopicTitle: Shelley Space Progam: Project Ike [(All Stock) Starts @ 8 PM EDT/5 PM PDT]

Articles.Content:
So I'm here again to tell you about my Friday Night adventures. Built my station, got Expedition II on the station last Friday, and now I am going to the Mun! Going to build and test out a Mun rocket to advance the cause of science and of course having a few while doing so. If you want to come hang out while I drink and do space feel free!

Shelley Space Program
